description: We feature a wide selection of commercial outdoor rattan garden and patio furniture at JB Commercial.  Our products have been selected and specifically designed for outdoor all weather applications, and are a great addition to any beer garden, hotels, terrace or outdoor seating area. Included in our range you will find quality rattan weave sets in various colours with cushions, coffee tables and loungers to complete the look. All items which contain foam and/or fabric are CRIB 5 Certified unless otherwise stated.
